description: Get all Application Insights web tests defined for the specified component.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.

api_version.description: The API version to use for this operation.

subscription_id.description: The ID of the target subscription.

value.description: Set of Application Insights web test definitions.

nextlink.description: The link to get the next part of the returned list of web tests, should the return set be too large for a single request. May be null.

component_name.description: The name of the Application Insights component resource.
